items.title: 'It's safe now': See students pulled from rubble of collapsed school
items.description: Dramatic rescue footage shows the boys in Indonesia pulled to safety after their school collapsed.

items.title: Activists say Gaza flotilla circled by Israeli warship
items.description: The Global Sumud Flotilla accused an Israeli vessel of steering "dangerously close" to one of its boats.

items.title: Munich Oktoberfest to re-open after fatal house fire and bomb threat
items.description: The annual beer festival was closed for several hours because of possible links to an explosion and fire.

items.title: Internet access returns to Afghanistan after Taliban blackout
items.description: A 48-hour shutdown imposed by the Taliban government hit firms, flights and risked further isolating women.

items.title: Danish PM calls for strong answer from EU leaders to Russia's hybrid attacks
items.description: Copenhagen is on alert as EU leaders discuss boosting their defences in response to disruption from drones and Russian war planes.
